heading: Championâ€™s Demise Dungeon Guide
content: Champion's Demise is an good dungeon featuring one of the best aspects, the . It has great monster families making it a good candidate for consecutive Nightmare Dungeon runs. However, the layout has lots of backtracking, slowing down overall completion time. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
